descCRN['10481&TermDescription=Fall%202017'] = '<p>Notes:<br />*First Year Course only, first day attendance required*<br/>This course provides an introduction to the handling, analysis, and interpretation of the big datasets now routinely being collected in science, commerce, and government. Students achieve facility with a sophisticated, technical computing environment. The course aligns with techniques being used in several courses in the natural and social sciences, statistics, and mathematics. The course is intended to be accessible to all students, regardless of background. (4 credits)</p>';
