descCRN['10621&TermDescription=Fall%202017'] = '<p>Notes:<br />A multidisciplinary investigation of behavior and the nervous system. Particular emphasis is placed on human processes of perception, cognition, learning, memory, and language. This course also serves as the introductory course for the neuroscience studies major. (4 credits)</p>';
